data.description: Welcome all buyers! This rare free standing-detached 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has been completely renovated with great attention to detail and maintained with meticulous care. Charming home full of character offers appliances, beautiful kitchen cabinets and refrigerator. This home also offers a main floor bedroom with a connecting full bath and 2 closets, wood flooring throughout the first floor, washer/dryer on the main floor, full basement, ceiling fans, large bright windows and built-in alarm system. Journey upstairs and you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms and additional full bath with wall to wall carpeting. Step into the backyard and you will find customized paving throughout and image relaxing in your own reserved oasis. Newly finished basement with a bilco doors as another means of egress. Convenient to TempleU, shopping, public transportation, 4 blocks from Shriner's Hospital and TempleU Hospital, parks, Route 611-(Broad Street), Route 1 and more. Schedule to your showing today!
